{"tid":1444884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真。時代革命？","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:43:36.000Z","uid":37897,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14ff7988382d36d789e925405583358e44d4a6c0","tid":1444884,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣發夢覺得和理非點升級既作用唔大？<br />\n<br />\n唔好反對和理非，支持大家既理念，各有各做。但係真係拎住香港命脈既係商，既得利益者又唔會放棄自己既野同你反政府，罷工又堵路擾民多， 所謂既成本增加又落曬市民到。當年黑人罷工抗爭成功係因為佢地係勞動人口既主幹，同時佢地亦唔係既得利益者是可以齊心合力，但香港唔同，事實上2個月黎既抗爭對香港經濟影響微乎其微，除左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗既樓價</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n宜家警察都開始be water，私家車快閃，入黑開始涼先同你玩對峙，消耗戰成果下降<br />\n<br />\n懇請各位勇武手足做好心理準備，真係hit（fire） and run， 唔係smoke and escape。<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2226f03c94ff6adecb7d9427f39682252959b0b0","tid":1444884,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7a84a97a5a4c1b3ed817ee1e1ea9b9b5565bcf4","tid":1444884,"uid":191642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"就算出埋老解感覺香港D樓都唔會跌好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf39034ed18e8030ae8fbf6def3d580cde50b62","tid":1444884,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"aad922070fdf736142b87f9d7c268ec9d8c741c4","tid":1444884,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:33:08.000Z","msg":"希望大家討論下和理非同勇武以後既路線，見到tst個女仕真係好心痛"},{"pid":"c184d95e8d6c2d85fc134ffb3425ed9e72cbccfe","tid":1444884,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"你老母班撚樣係地鐵站都放催淚彈"},{"pid":"5541451d437e80cf5992781741f05b8a1f5db90a","tid":1444884,"uid":264996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"